    <description>
      Serilog and Application Insights for ASP.NET Core: telemetry registration, W3C correlation initializers, and ILogger extensions for events, metrics, dependencies, and requests.
    </description>
    <tags>serilog application-insights aspnetcore logging telemetry dotnet csharp</tags>
